IMPORTANT NOTE ON INDIGENOUS KNOWLEDGE

Content within the pilots/ directory may contain or reference indigenous ecological
knowledge contributed through participatory processes. Use of such content must
respect the data sovereignty frameworks described in this repository and the
governance structures of the contributing communities. When in doubt, contact
the relevant community representatives before reusing pilot-specific content.
